Gustaf Adolf Oscar Fredrik Arthur Edmund Bernadotte av Sverige, Duke of Västerbotten, was born 22 April 1906 in Stockholm, Sweden to Gustaf VI Adolf av Sverige (1882-1973) and Margaret of Connaught (1882-1920) and died 26 January 1947 Copenhagen, Denmark of airplane crash. He married Sibylla von Sachsen-Coburg und Gotha (1908-1972) 19 October 1932 in Coburg, Germany.
